trans-unit.source: Defines an interface that can be implemented in a type in order to preload the type in an ASP.NET application that is running on IIS 7.0.
trans-unit.target: Define uma interface que pode ser implementada em um tipo a fim de pré-carregar o tipo em um aplicativo ASP.NET que está sendo executado no IIS 7.0.

trans-unit.source: This interface is intended primarily for use by WCF applications that are non-HTTP applications.
trans-unit.target: Essa interface destina-se principalmente para uso por aplicativos WCF que aplicativos não HTTP.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET developers who want to preload ASP.NET Web applications should use the simulated HTTP requests in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] combined with the `Application_Start` method in the Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: Os desenvolvedores do ASP.NET que deseja pré-carregar aplicativos Web ASP.NET devem usar as solicitações HTTP simuladas em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] combinado com o `Application_Start` método no arquivo global. asax.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient> type and its methods apply only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[win7](~/includes/win7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient> tipo e seus métodos que se aplicam apenas a aplicativos executados em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] e [!INCLUDE[win7](~/includes/win7-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This parameter can be <see langword="null" /> or an empty array.
trans-unit.target: Esse parâmetro pode ser <see langword="null" /> ou uma matriz vazia.

trans-unit.source: Provides initialization data that is required in order to preload the application.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados de inicialização que são necessários para pré-carregar o aplicativo.

trans-unit.source: The value of `parameters` can be `null`, a zero-length array, or a populated array.
trans-unit.target: O valor de `parameters` pode ser `null`, uma matriz de comprimento zero ou uma matriz preenchida.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient> type and its methods apply only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[win7](~/includes/win7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient> tipo e seus métodos que se aplicam apenas a aplicativos executados em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] e [!INCLUDE[win7](~/includes/win7-md.md)].
